中至少有1.3亿女性失踪。#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/O3bBSi6Fzl","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"女孩面臨的障礙從子宮開始。由於針對胎兒性別進行的選擇性人工流產和忽視，世界人口中至少有1.3億女性失蹤。#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/O3bBSi6Fzl","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447743889293590533","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447743889293590533/","title":"Societies that oppress women are far more likely to be violent and unstable. Policymakers who fail to consider the interests of half the population cannot hope to understand the world #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/wggcrKeCRL","date":"October 12, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-12T02:41:58.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-12 02:41","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447743889293590533","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447743889293590533","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":225,"views":null,"sharedCount":52,"likeCount":121,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"女性を抑圧する社会は、暴力的で不安定な社会になる可能性がはるかに高い。人口の半分の利益を考慮しない政策立案者には、世界を理解することは望めません #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/wggcrKeCRL","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"压迫妇女的社会更可能是暴力和不稳定的。不考虑一半人口利益的政策制定者不可能希望了解这个世界#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/wggcrKeCRL","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"壓迫婦女的社會更可能是暴力和不穩定的。不考慮一半人口利益的政策制定者不可能希望瞭解這個世界#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/wggcrKeCRL","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447697019708059649","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447697019708059649/","title":"Researchers have found that sexist customs are highly correlated with violent instability in a country. Various lessons can be drawn from this #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/gk3mXEdZia","date":"October 11, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-11T23:30:44.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-11 23:30","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447697019708059649","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447697019708059649","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":154,"views":null,"sharedCount":33,"likeCount":88,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"研究者たちは、性差別的な習慣が、その国の暴力的な不安定さと高い相関関係があることを発見しました。この#BrighterFutureForGirlsから様々な教訓が得られます https://t.co/gk3mXEdZia","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"研究人员发现，性别歧视的习俗与一个国家的暴力不稳定高度相关。从这个#为女孩创造更光明的未来#中可以得出各种教训 https://t.co/gk3mXEdZia","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"研究人員發現，性別歧視的習俗與一個國家的暴力不穩定高度相關。從這個#爲女孩創造更光明的未來#中可以得出各種教訓 https://t.co/gk3mXEdZia","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447654773193330692","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447654773193330692/","title":"“It seems as if the surest way to curse one’s nation is to subordinate its women,” say the authors of a study that ranks 176 countries for misogyny #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/pVYbNXwy5B","date":"October 11, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-11T20:20:06.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-11 20:20","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447654773193330692","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447654773193330692","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":180,"views":null,"sharedCount":43,"likeCount":94,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"「自分の国を呪う最も確実な方法は、その国の女性を従属させることであるかのようだ」と、176カ国の女性差別度をランキングした研究の著者は言う #BlighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/pVYbNXwy5B","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"\"似乎诅咒自己国家的最可靠方式是使其妇女处于从属地位，\"一项研究的作者说，该研究对176个国家的厌女症进行了排名#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/pVYbNXwy5B。","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"\"似乎詛咒自己國家的最可靠方式是使其婦女處於從屬地位，\"一項研究的作者說，該研究對176個國家的厭女症進行了排名#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/pVYbNXwy5B。","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447592395760181250","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447592395760181250/","title":"Researchers have found a strong statistical link between pre-modern attitudes to women and violent political instability #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/ogacSwRCWv","date":"October 11, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-11T17:45:05.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-11 17:45","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447592395760181250","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447592395760181250","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":151,"views":null,"sharedCount":37,"likeCount":77,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"研究者たちは、前近代的な女性への態度と暴力的な政治的不安定さとの間に、統計的に強い関連性があることを発見しました。 #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/ogacSwRCWv","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"研究人员发现，在前现代对妇女的态度和暴力政治不稳定之间存在着强有力的统计学联系 #女孩的光明未来 https://t.co/ogacSwRCWv","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"研究人員發現，在前現代對婦女的態度和暴力政治不穩定之間存在着強有力的統計學聯繫 #女孩的光明未來 https://t.co/ogacSwRCWv","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447607968707616774","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447607968707616774/","title":"Educating girls makes them richer, healthier and more free. And their children inherit these advantages #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/XBexsXJqGG","date":"October 11, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-11T17:30:29.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-11 17:30","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447607968707616774","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447607968707616774","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":179,"views":null,"sharedCount":39,"likeCount":101,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"女子を教育することで、より豊かで健康的で自由な生活を送ることができます。そして、彼女たちの子どもたちはこれらの利点を受け継ぐのです #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/XBexsXJqGG","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"教育女孩使她们更富有、更健康、更自由。而她们的孩子也会继承这些优势#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/XBexsXJqGG","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"教育女孩使她們更富有、更健康、更自由。而她們的孩子也會繼承這些優勢#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/XBexsXJqGG","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"TweetPost-1447575589746094088","excerpt":"","slug":"/tweet/1447575589746094088/","title":"A fifth of the world’s young women were married before the age of 18. Child brides are more likely to drop out of school, less able to stand up to abusive husbands and less likely to raise healthy, well-educated children #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/YNJpJ4HyCw","date":"October 11, 2021","dateISO":"2021-10-11T15:28:47.000Z","datetime":"2021-10-11 15:28","tags":["BrighterFutureForGirls","tweet"],"image":null,"imageAlt":null,"__typename":"SocialMediaPost","provider":"Twitter","thirdPartyId":"1447575589746094088","url":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist/statuses/1447575589746094088","originalUrl":null,"imageRemote":null,"video":null,"channel":null,"channelUrl":null,"author":"The Economist","authorUrl":"https://twitter.com/TheEconomist","authorImageRemote":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/879361767914262528/HdRauDM-.jpg","authorImage":null,"authorSlug":"TheEconomist","score":153,"views":null,"sharedCount":41,"likeCount":71,"sharedContent":null,"parent":{"localize":[{"locale":"ja","full_text":"世界の若い女性の5分の1が18歳未満で結婚しています。子どもの花嫁は、学校を中退する可能性が高く、虐待する夫に立ち向かうことができず、健康で教育水準の高い子どもを育てることができません #BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/YNJpJ4HyCw","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh","full_text":"世界上有五分之一的年轻女性在18岁之前结婚。童养媳更有可能辍学，更无法抵御丈夫的虐待，更不可能养育出健康、受过良好教育的孩子#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/YNJpJ4HyCw","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null},{"locale":"zh-Hant","full_text":"世界上有五分之一的年輕女性在18歲之前結婚。童養媳更有可能輟學，更無法抵禦丈夫的虐待，更不可能養育出健康、受過良好教育的孩子#BrighterFutureForGirls https://t.co/YNJpJ4HyCw","quoted_status_full_text":null,"retweeted_status_full_text":null}]}},{"id":"Twee